Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}偶然の虚飾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:59.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}喰い合いを急ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:05.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}死んだ眼の獣よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:09.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Never be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}感情何度込めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:18.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}勝率は上がらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Believe in my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:24.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}純粋で美麗な勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}さあルーレット止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:30.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}非情に選ぶがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:57.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}判定はただ敢え無く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}敗者は消え　勝者には　Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:08.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}次が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}そしてルーレット廻る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:15.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}勝利さえ許さず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}For my love, I'll bet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:22.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}一度捨てた命に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:27.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}足掻いてはいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now take this. My life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:33.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}潔く美しく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}さあルーレット廻れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:39.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}私を嗤うがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:50.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}佇む一枚のチップ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:55.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}譲ることなく一つを守る
